Open Windows Security -> App & browser control -> Exploit Protection Settings and set the following to On by default:

-Force randomization for images (Mandatory ALSR)
-Randomize memory allocations (Bottom-up ASLR)
-High-entropy ALSR


See: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/security/threat-protection/overview-of-threat-mitigations-in-windows-10#address-space-layout-randomization
